<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Annulation de Trajet</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 40px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 35px 30px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
        }
        .content p { margin: 0 0 16px 0; }
        .details-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .details-box strong {
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 150px;
        }
        .value {
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .details-box hr {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            color: #666;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 3px solid #667eea;
        }
        .footer-logo {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">KOWIHAN</div>
            <h1>{{subject}}</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Bonjour,</p>
            <p>Veuillez noter qu'un trajet sur votre ligne a été annulé :</p>

            <div class="details-box">
                <strong>Ligne :</strong>
                <span class="value">{{routeName}}</span>
                <hr>
                <strong>Arrêt concerné :</strong>
                <span class="value">{{stopName}}</span>
                <hr>
                <strong>Heure prévue :</strong>
                <span class="value">{{scheduledTime}}</span>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 25px;"><strong>Raison de l'annulation :</strong> {{reason}}</p>
            <p>Nous nous excusons sincèrement pour la gêne occasionnée.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 25px;">Cordialement,<br><strong>L'équipe Kowihan</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-logo">KOWIHAN</div>
            Votre satisfaction est notre priorité.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>